data.description: Come see your dream home. This beautiful 4 bed 2 bath  3 car garage home is located in a quiet securely gated subdivision just minutes from the suncoast. Perfect for a family or to be used as a rental.This home features a combination living room/dining room, large eat in kitchen with 42in maple cabinets and SS appliances overlooking family room. Master suite features walk in closet, dual vanities and separate garden tub and shower, and covered lanai. Fenced Yard. 2,384 Living sqft, 3,340 Total sqft. Conveniently located in gated Sterling Hill with 2 club houses, 2 swimming pools, 2 playgrounds, exercise facility, tennis, basketball, volleyball and dog run.
